Times being what they are,

11
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,458
we've extended offers
to foreign specialist

12
00:03:18,541 --> 00:03:23,000
with good references as well
as the usual D11 and SAS crowd.

13
00:03:23,083 --> 00:03:24,500
I trust you.

14
