We found a report from
one of our embassy men.

15
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:50,666
They found a
factory in Hong Kong

16
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:53,791
that has been producing
quantities of the freak chip.

17
00:03:53,875 --> 00:03:55,875
The Hong Kong Police
executed a compulsory

18
00:03:55,958 --> 00:03:58,750
investigation into
the matter, but...

19
